{
  "stem": "1338.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My uncle was reading-- the Berlin [GERMAN], and said that the people who produced Goethe and Beethoven couldn't be that bad.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought, for Pete's sake, where was he for the last eight years?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, doesn't he ever read anything?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Doesn't he ever see anything?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why I'm saying I wasn't very-- maybe I was always analytically inclined, and didn't kid myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Remember that older people always-- like in the army, generals always fight the last war, not the next one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same thing with people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always view the times with the experience of the last war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And remember, World War I, the Germans were the nice guys, and the Russians were the bad guys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you couldn't get it out of their blood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while, to me, it was quite clear, I was not burdened with the experience.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Experience can be a lot of burden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only time I remember that one of our relatives was an alderman of the city, and quite prominent, decided to leave to go to Palestine-- and actually moved in '36-- showed up in '37 for a visit and told my mother, give me your son if you don't want to come.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the only time I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[WHISPERS] Well, forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a rhetorical question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But-- but anyway, so that is the only thing I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think the-- the process of-- of the Nazi occupation and all the things that preceded it is a process of-- of creeping.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything in life is creeping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't-- nothing happens, unless you have some historical event, like a catastrophic volcano disruption or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything in human life, including the stock market, is a gradual process.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
